<exercise id="fs-id1172098258754">
<problem id="fs-id1172100536988">
<para id="fs-id1172098390769">Granulocytes are which type of cell?</para>
<list id="fs-id1172098749197" list-type="enumerated" number-style="upper-alpha">
<item>lymphocyte</item>
